The Schachbundesliga Championship is an extra tournament to determine the champion of 2020 while the regular league has been suspended and will continue in spring 2021.

Players receive 90 minutes for the first 40 moves followed by 30 minutes for the rest of the game, with a 30-second increment from move one. Official website: www.schachbundesliga.de
